{"h5d7d20aeg3dceg4eb8gacb6gcf5e72b14f76": ["See! It squealed!", "fc3116bd-4ed0-4246-a7db-64b3a0fd48d1", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "e38dd723-59a3-2163-be4d-3dd3760987fa"], "hf253964bgc7fcg42dcgb973g18c8813dfde0": ["Hit it again!", "dff4432a-85b4-4d5c-95b5-6d1179dbabf4", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "b4341248-2aea-e0d6-5ed2-0576610dcba1"], "h87974de5g5b20g43bcg957dg6acffeacd9b6": ["Keep yer hand steady, Three.", "6e4dd891-7bfe-4656-a9a0-ecf0916fd8f0", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "5eb36859-0cee-76c1-c078-486f04406410"], "h06d46719g19d7g4809ga55dg671a3c48ab07": ["Hmph.", "fc3116bd-4ed0-4246-a7db-64b3a0fd48d1", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "51cfd355-1724-e0de-d976-cc3c04f911b5"], "h817eb24cgd516g4366g9d5ag1bc132a0bda3": ["Stop them. Free me.", "7628bc0e-52b8-42a7-856a-13a6fd413323", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "d4012bcb-4c89-32ad-1304-4e29dc7dc12a"], "hb027dd0fg76f8g4f6dgbdd6g793ee74bedcc": ["Again! Again! Make it squeal again!", "dff4432a-85b4-4d5c-95b5-6d1179dbabf4", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "c700767a-58f7-9d4e-39f1-33bfd168987a"], "h8416ab95g8defg4623g8e2agadca584c5d42": ["What the hells are you doing?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "7375590f-fbf6-7dae-e6e6-6dc5d148e74c"], "h06423d5ag5fe0g400dg82f3gd31dff50bb2f": ["We're juicing it up. The beast came in here with those robbers. Killed Dink, and Mince, too. ", "6e4dd891-7bfe-4656-a9a0-ecf0916fd8f0", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "d7332e47-3ba4-f7a9-df6f-8642de696225"], "h36907145gf4fbg436agbb9dg0977d1b7a5aa": ["Boss's thinkin' of servin' it to the worgs.", "6e4dd891-7bfe-4656-a9a0-ecf0916fd8f0", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "7ab5a6aa-f352-fde8-ed2c-213d926b7cee"], "h02d77cd7g6c26g490agaa75g3ea3c5d629a5": ["<i>And </i>it makes funny noises.", "fc3116bd-4ed0-4246-a7db-64b3a0fd48d1", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "e6280db9-523e-30f1-20fa-c981b3d051d5"], "hccae558dg84efg433egb46dgb2aed2aa9b36": ["We made it squeal!", "dff4432a-85b4-4d5c-95b5-6d1179dbabf4", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "54021fbb-37cc-d297-9f25-c04026f65e20"], "h20a13652g23a5g4805g824cg1b33d7f9ad79": ["Look, look, you'll see. Gimme that rock. I'll show ya!", "fc3116bd-4ed0-4246-a7db-64b3a0fd48d1", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "205786ee-439c-3ae4-b8f8-5ae4b8e1ba98"], "h265eb72eg3be8g4bfdg91a6g535f48c5c146": ["Go on, then. Keep at it.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "b4831103-960e-dd59-5ce3-f4ad717cce0c"], "haf9ca87dg38deg4578g9b30gec5320cbbf3d": ["Leave him alone!", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "1f167c4b-8164-8d34-a812-062c9ef91ae4"], "h76c15720g0837g4007gb8b1g8da4d97e4129": ["What're ya - get lost if you can't stand a bit of rough-housin'.", "6e4dd891-7bfe-4656-a9a0-ecf0916fd8f0", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "8fd1d368-26f5-8cf1-07b0-b0cccfde53f4"], "he670ea09g67ffg4284g9475g2b6d7b8f6ff5": ["Release me.", "7628bc0e-52b8-42a7-856a-13a6fd413323", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "fdd6f2bd-2bcc-a6d0-d666-f1bce0a08a66"], "h7567b605g5408g4fb7gb274g74c59a871d6d": ["Get rid of <i>them</i>.", "7628bc0e-52b8-42a7-856a-13a6fd413323", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "c7e31aec-1a2d-6b0d-5bea-d974ee5627ed"], "he5977ac0ge9f3g44cfg84e7gbabf127e8408": ["<i>Attack the goblins.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "0197619e-5e17-6e43-0314-b97eabe6659e"], "ha05d1608gce9eg44e5gb97cg60816b431ce6": ["Time for blood.", "7628bc0e-52b8-42a7-856a-13a6fd413323", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "7f5fe54a-4c9d-6167-b8e6-560ae061f36b"], "h4298fb94g233dg496ag82d9gacc3643b7bf5": ["*Roar!*", "7628bc0e-52b8-42a7-856a-13a6fd413323", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "0ae5259a-dce4-085a-2341-0e9b34f2f950"], "hccc7adfeg5239g4c1aga8b6g10e7576bb4de": ["<i>Throw a rock at the bear.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "d5b5c021-a843-3f03-ffb3-8dfc2ffb0acf"], "h8a81b728g0abcg498cgb4b0g331639fdff9e": ["You chose. You die with them.", "7628bc0e-52b8-42a7-856a-13a6fd413323", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "b1b3de26-73cd-cab5-5d47-908323fc5c56"], "h126f2ea7g8a94g434dg9684gbcf178cc3e2c": ["<i>Leave the bear to the goblin's mercy.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "751d9c00-af8f-d15d-406f-c2fcedb0d927"], "hd9e7b939g0ae9g465agb7beg66a0317cd8b9": ["*Growl.*", "7628bc0e-52b8-42a7-856a-13a6fd413323", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "c0850e34-17d0-08dd-779a-66ad8251bf87"], "h5692ea5fg4eebg4dd0gab50g7bc4b5c95534": ["How about a taste of your own medicine?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "99e51017-2aac-94bf-941c-ae1330ef46ad"], "hc931475aga0b5g49d0gb594g62322db35458": ["He's helpless. Let him go.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "0eb1b6a4-06ff-97ed-20dc-bcce3e567c94"], "h1cdbcce9g3121g4c5fgb204geacb3da22d69": ["It's stayin' right 'ere. The beast came in here with those robbers. Killed Dink, and Mince, too. ", "6e4dd891-7bfe-4656-a9a0-ecf0916fd8f0", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "b8d61d9a-f8a2-573f-e574-815c26122447"], "h6e5dbf00gc398g41a8gafbfg00ed3108b0d1": ["Boss's thinkin' of servin' it to the worgs. But first, Three, more stones. Make it nice an' bloody.", "6e4dd891-7bfe-4656-a9a0-ecf0916fd8f0", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "7af0ae3a-3a00-c96d-a5d8-599978b37a5e"], "h3fe0e396g9d21g4e5cg8122gfb1151cb03ae": ["Yeah! Hit its head! I wanna hear more noises!", "dff4432a-85b4-4d5c-95b5-6d1179dbabf4", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "cc6b7ab3-20a5-8e52-5881-bacf71f7cb5b"], "h811c1530g753eg427ega2f1g6281b52f90e9": ["*The mark glows, but you feel nothing in response. Your illithid power is beyond reach until you rest.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "1ab53902-49ac-6c47-f979-fb74bc06a490"], "h0fa7a8b6ga948g4bf0gb079ga7880d484b7b": ["Stop it!", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "fef86aa4-eee5-dedb-c5f6-531dcbd46a32"], "hdbb2117fg50b0g4a9fg9f60gf5d90bff19b8": ["How dare ya.", "6e4dd891-7bfe-4656-a9a0-ecf0916fd8f0", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "65ce5674-ef91-6f70-83b3-0217b18ced57"], "h451e7715g4d18g4bd6g87acg5773ab9d53ce": ["Go on, then. Aim for his eye.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "46a286b9-04da-58b1-9c71-69c611fd9e2f"], "hd9653f79g9efeg4beeg90d1ge50d8f74f42f": ["I'm putting an end to this. Now.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "ff9d71c7-4589-3f63-8176-b735be9dc9b7"], "h8218286dgee4eg456ega877g386ad357d7c9": ["Time for blood.", "7628bc0e-52b8-42a7-856a-13a6fd413323", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "daa73987-9276-e38f-b407-1d40de210a96"], "h45bbcc99g2267g4d67gb3feg3cb4fdcf02aa": ["*Roar!*", "7628bc0e-52b8-42a7-856a-13a6fd413323", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "c8ad1b5d-6693-077a-64be-01c204d04484"], "h557e0ea9gdb26g48d5g87ccg7af12be9cbeb": ["You <i>dare </i>disobey a drow?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "37394e07-5d16-9d47-9070-d3ed473726ca"], "h55993e05g2840g4a22gb961g937efb518acf": ["I - I mean no disrespect, just - these are the boss's orders. I can't let it out for no one but a True Soul.", "6e4dd891-7bfe-4656-a9a0-ecf0916fd8f0", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "a79fa97e-33da-2b21-ddb6-d1538402c5b0"], "hffd0a83cgf5e1g4d6agb7a4g5cd18d08685b": ["Then I'll just have to kill you.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "6b19677b-a5b3-27ce-6fa4-17af623501c8"], "hf5209d08gbc9ag40b6ga567gee4512d00c0b": ["Fine. Do what you want with him.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "b5df2df0-5e5e-8772-96ae-80798866c5e4"], "h92bef8e0g70b4g4825gbed9gd35371217dbe": ["You <i>will </i>free the beast for me.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "7e6e7fe2-8f86-4fe3-2ba6-25879b8d8d33"], "h1bba0b4bg15ccg4820ga953g282b41098e6c": ["Oh, you're - uh, y-yes, of course.", "6e4dd891-7bfe-4656-a9a0-ecf0916fd8f0", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "e5b928f9-c7d3-550e-dd62-2e8719c23009"], "hfceba196g628eg4743gb97cg93a8d3cfd854": ["Y-yes, of course.", "6e4dd891-7bfe-4656-a9a0-ecf0916fd8f0", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "89b124f5-4486-f30f-83b0-d963c8a3f002"], "h313e7d06g5ae6g4f67gaddcga8bf86f07c6c": ["*A shiver runs across your mind... you feel sated.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "ba186175-a4d4-4adb-5944-b88ba73da13e"], "hd82f5e3fg7618g4ae9gaaffg3a1804128070": ["But - but I wanna hear it <i>squeal</i>!", "dff4432a-85b4-4d5c-95b5-6d1179dbabf4", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "35dae024-f22b-caa9-2c08-74005f95c6ef"], "he1a57f95g7ab7g403dg9ebbg0877d73ad3c9": ["One! That's a True Soul you're talkin' to. Show some respect!", "6e4dd891-7bfe-4656-a9a0-ecf0916fd8f0", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "fae7935f-3081-c95e-8fb5-275761f2ae12"], "hdc4be8c6gd01eg4f22gb916gcfd9f0cd3069": ["S-sorry, Ma'am. I'll open the cage for ya.", "6e4dd891-7bfe-4656-a9a0-ecf0916fd8f0", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "fc9a5916-112c-55ff-4333-5a4e3f77e2c3"], "hc4c6dc7cg5952g4445g85fbg20412f3b22e5": ["S-sorry, sir. I'll open the cage for ya.", "6e4dd891-7bfe-4656-a9a0-ecf0916fd8f0", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "fc9a5916-112c-55ff-4333-5a4e3f77e2c3"], "hb682ca3cg469ag426dga351g602489754278": ["*Something stirs deep within you, hungry and alert... it's taking something you'll never get back.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "c5d4349b-1f0d-cb60-95eb-6a8823d085c3"], "hede4375fg3c43g43begb508g38365a03b2e6": ["*Your mind lurches, reeling suddenly as if... bitten.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "7ace91e9-ad3f-bde8-5373-61ba922d2afd"], "hbc39f95dg0a3ag46begacbdgdb43ab1eda22": ["*A shadow swims across your vision, and a familiar voice tells you to be calm. You are loved.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "00d6a308-5484-fc54-248f-6f9f1fcb8ba3"], "hef3f4908gffe6g4e71g908bg26d934de2547": ["*Your blood runs quicker, feeding the gnawing absence at the centre of your mind.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "f0365eda-9243-c350-b5cb-9a366eba14b1"], "h90fd6bbcge855g4b62g936ag6ae3b37dca2e": ["*The presence deep in your mind is awake, unblinking. This is it. A single word pervades your consciousness: 'Soon'.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "fadfa04e-a44c-a8e6-f2e1-85673824ac20"], "h50c110bega9a7g4104gad65g26c9331079a6": ["*Your mind is full, bursting with ecstasy and terror. Finally, it is coming. You are becoming.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "adb1b734-0a76-c1a0-d2c6-3805ef99f271"], "hc85691b4g41b9g4fdeg880egc321f0bc5a5c": ["You <i>will </i>free the beast for me.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "8bfa9c73-8719-1141-8b74-788dad81babf"], "hfb382810ga7e1g4e55g87f3g8d2bb820cc40": ["*A strange symbol glows, marked on their flesh, and something within you stirs in response.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "6a68d5f5-794a-c0a1-d7fe-a33b3f9eac52"], "h57cd2e12g0e07g41e3ga4d6g5021432b0745": ["Let him out. I'll take care of the beast.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "52151704-7204-a9b3-2df5-af9095246cd7"], "hd896e0b5gf2fbg471eg87c1ga54a803df9ea": ["Let him out. I'll take care of the beast.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "d7bf12bf-e5d9-1c3d-63aa-25af460d88be"], "hb9bbec03ga516g4df6g8a5dgc9e7e6ab5b57": ["*As the symbol glows, power courses through you. <i>Authority</i>.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "8316ac88-3380-054a-2b4f-8f7b3f723e4f"], "hebcaaaabg8a3dg4b9egb4bdgc601c6e27261": ["Sharper stones might cut through all that fur.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "3e5cb0fa-17b5-b623-7f83-7b1099e3edc5"], "h54428579g22b5g4404gba7agaefbfe7ae2c5": ["Ha!", "fc3116bd-4ed0-4246-a7db-64b3a0fd48d1", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "e631ae73-5b3d-2f75-3c6f-77e3842d31a2"], "h2946d9c8gbc4ag457fgbdd8g06ee02fe0016": ["No. Why?", "7628bc0e-52b8-42a7-856a-13a6fd413323", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "d346c26c-8414-1036-1066-81fb80377d75"], "h612d86f1gcefbg4915ga5f6g9763330aebe9": ["*Whimper.*", "7628bc0e-52b8-42a7-856a-13a6fd413323", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "b13ff598-0c8e-aba1-0724-32715b7c44ec"], "hc4d28694gfa8fg48degb20dga6d43e39ce37": ["<i>Turn away.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "5e43db36-0271-ba49-eb9f-887c424ddefc"], "h0704a773g02e6g4e6fga197g1280ed6178ef": ["No. Free me.", "7628bc0e-52b8-42a7-856a-13a6fd413323", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "a5166dd7-d0d7-b487-dcbc-bc84f6a9812a"], "hcd5a1750g922dg48f7gb902g48e256f6887e": ["That's it. I'm putting a stop to this.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "da082d76-71a1-521f-c60f-bcb9cbfabdfd"], "hd797fbf4g8cacg4e89gb481gb179cecf172e": ["<i>Throw a rock at the bear.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "3ddb52f5-ee0a-11fa-5a91-79fae812f2c8"], "h017a53a7gd21ag4f6ag8ea5gfe8966ae5c78": ["You chose. You die with them.", "7628bc0e-52b8-42a7-856a-13a6fd413323", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "811fcfa8-a3de-963e-cfff-c022c3498505"], "h809d7261gd65fg4765gba50g708f8b0b9d39": ["*Growl.*", "7628bc0e-52b8-42a7-856a-13a6fd413323", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDialogWithBear.html", "7468032b-3ca6-a2ee-f62f-075dc1415959"], "h5d037d50g9fccg48a5g9dc8g007cb9c901fe": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_WolfPens_GroupDi